        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 56. Sagola species in the notabilis species-group. Habitus, dorsal views: a) S. notabilis, b) S. monstrosa, c) S. tararuaensis. Aedeagi, dorsal views: d) S. notabilis, e) S. monstrosa, f) S. tararuaensis. S. monstrosa, male: g) Antenna, h) Dorsal surface of head, i) Ventral surface of head, j) Hind leg, lateral view, k) Hind claw, lateral view, l) Abdomen, ventral view. Scale bars a–c = 1 mm, d–l = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4907888/files/figure.png" .

